properties.doc: The resource-specific properties for this resource.

type.name: StandbyVirtualMachinePoolRuntimeViewProperties
type.doc: Contains information about a standby pool as last known by the StandbyPool resource provider.

properties.name: instanceCountSummary
properties.doc: A list containing the counts of virtual machines in each possible power state for each zone if enabled, as known by the StandbyPool resource provider. If zones are not enabled on the attached VMSS, the list will contain a single entry without zone values. Note: any resources in the Running state may still be installing extensions / not fully provisioned.

valueType.name: StandbyVirtualMachineInstanceCountSummary
valueType.doc: Contains the counts of VMs in each power state in a given zone, fault domain, as known by the StandbyPool resource provider. Note: any resources in the Running state may still be installing extensions / not fully provisioned.

properties.name: zone
properties.doc: The zone that the provided counts are in. It will not have a value if zones are not enabled on the attached VMSS.

properties.name: StandbyVirtualMachineInstanceCountsByState
properties.doc: The count of pooled virtual machines in each state for the given zone.

valueType.name: PoolVirtualMachineStateCount
valueType.doc: Displays the counts of pooled virtual machines in each state, as known by the StandbyPool resource provider.

properties.name: state
properties.doc: The state that the pooled virtual machines count is for.

properties.name: count
properties.doc: The count of pooled virtual machines in the given state.

properties.name: status
properties.doc: Display status of the standby pool

properties.name: code
properties.doc: Displays the healthy state of the StandbyPool.

properties.name: message
properties.doc: Displays the StandbyPool health state details.

properties.name: provisioningState
properties.doc: Displays the provisioning state of the standby pool

properties.name: prediction
properties.doc: Displays prediction information of the standby pool

type.name: StandbyVirtualMachinePoolPrediction
type.doc: Displays prediction information of the standby pool.

properties.name: forecastValues
properties.doc: Displays the forecast information of the standby pool.

type.name: StandbyVirtualMachinePoolForecastValues
type.doc: Displays the forecast information of the standby pool.

properties.name: instancesRequestedCount
properties.doc: Displays the predicted count of instances to be requested from the standby pool.

properties.name: forecastStartTime
properties.doc: Displays the UTC timestamp of when the prediction was retrieved for the standby pool.

properties.name: forecastInfo
properties.doc: Displays additional information for the prediction of the standby pool.

properties.name: name
properties.doc: The unique identifier for the runtime view. The input string should be the word 'latest', which will get the latest runtime view of the pool, otherwise the request will fail with NotFound exception.
